I’ve been mulling over what to say for a few days now, and I’ve realized I can’t say enough. I owe so much to @postersandtoys @animalrummy and @ericgarza1201. Three of the most supportive people I’ve encountered in my life. I love y’all to death, and I’m so thankful for the opportunities you’ve given me and so many others, and for the community you created that we’ve all been so lucky to be a part of. I’ve got your back until the end. Xoxo

This Friday! We have a collaborative print series release by @sirmitchell and @reederone! Three total prints will be released online via reederone.shop (link in bio) from Dec 15th through Dec 17th. This is a time release, so all orders placed during the purchase window will be guaranteed — no limit on online orders. The prints will be numbered and signed by both artists! Printed by @staticmedium in Los Angeles!

In conjunction with the online sales, we will also be releasing two additional collaborative prints exclusively available at @staticmediums booth #1316 at this year’s @designercon from Dec 15th through Dec 17th. These prints are limited editions and are numbered and signed by both artists.

The prints sizes vary from 8”x10” to 8”x8” depending on the image.

Pictured above is Boxo III (Reeder Variant II) 
8”x8”
$60

Oh and did we mention the chase variant???
